  "rationale": "The source-balanced, frozen-encoder v13 candidate passed every aggregate gate except source-held-out field macro-F1. Aggregate source/class metrics show persistent domain rejection, so this predeclared run fine-tunes only the final two DINOv2 transformer blocks and final norm at a low learning rate. Equal expected sampling weight per licensed source prevents the large controlled and PLDD sources from dominating. Checkpoint selection uses pooled macro-F1 over declared source-disjoint field validation sources, with global validation macro-F1 as the tie-breaker.",
